(1) Compilation and installation instructions
---------------------------------------------

Be sure that you have downloaded, installed and configured Apache Maven properly:

http://maven.apache.org/

You may then compile the package by typing:

$ mvn clean install

at the command prompt.

(2) Running the Z80 testbench
-----------------------------

Chdir to the testbench directory and run the program with Maven exec plugin:

$ cd testbench/

$ mvn exec:java

(3) Running the Spectrum emulator
---------------------------------

Chdir to the Spectrum directory and run the program with Maven exec plugin:

$ cd spectrum/

$ mvn exec:java

It is possible to load and save Z80 and SNA snapshots by options listed in
the "File" menu.

For further details, see the source code.


Mikko Nummelin <mikko.nummelin@tkk.fi>

